# Changelog

## v0.3.8

*Release date: 10/01/2020*

* make subprocess usage compatible with python < 3.7

## v0.3.7

*Release date: 10/01/2020*

* fix minor bugs with `cath-cli ssap-batch`
* add tests

## v0.3.5

*Release date: 08/01/2020*

* update dependencies
* correct bug in `cath-align-scorecons` if old alignment does not have DOPS

## v0.3.4

*Release date: 07/01/2020*

* correct setup for namespace packages and tools

## v0.3.1

*Release date: 27/11/2019*

* correct setup for namespace packages

## v0.3.0

*Release date: 27/11/2019*

* move cathpy.* to cathpy.core.* (allow namespace packages)
* add `cath-cli`
* add batch processing for ssaps

## v0.2.2

*Release date: 11/10/2019*

* improved amino acid checks
* fixed bug with warning message when parsing stockholm alignments from string

## v0.2.1

*Release date: 21/06/2019*

* changed new_from_(file|string|io) to from_(file|string|io)
* cathpy.release container classes retrieve via primary key (eg. domainlist[0] === domainlist['1cukA01'])
* added codecov

## v0.1.14

*Release date: 20/06/2019*

* added `cathpy.release` to read/write/query CATH release files

## v0.1.13

*Release date: 12/06/2019*

* allow for null results from funfhmmer scan

## v0.1.12

*Release date: 30/05/2019*

* results from `align.get_meta_summary` now returns as AlignMetaSummary

## v0.1.11

*Release date: 30/05/2019*

* generate summary of alignment meta data `align.get_meta_summary`

## v0.1.10

*Release date: 21/05/2019*

* stockholm parser can now process meta data in Pfam alignments
* use `uid` rather than `id` in `cathpy.align`

## v0.1.9

*Release date: 16/05/2019*

* minor improvements to Sequence and Alignment
  * align.add_sequence() now accepts `offset`
  * len(Sequence) works as expected
  * Segment start/stop can be accessed with seg[0], seg[1]

## v0.1.8

*Release date: 09/05/2019*

* align:
  * handle `.gz` align files
  * use start/stop (in params) rather than start/end 

## v0.1.7

*Release date: 02/05/2019*

## v0.1.6

*Release date: 02/05/2019*

* funfhmmer:
  * allow custom queues
  * incorporate resolved scans

* Make sure matrix data is included in package

## v0.1.5

*Release date: 24/04/2019*

* Added required matrix data for `scorecons` binary

## v0.1.4

*Release date: 16/04/2019*

* Added binaries to allow scripts to work on Mac (darwin) and Linux

## v0.1.1

*Release date: 15/04/2019*

* Improved how version numbers are stored

## v0.1.0

*Release date: 15/04/2019*

### General

* Improved handling of STOCKHOLM parser (f52b9a1, 4fc0069)
* Added Sphinx docs
* Refactor `cathpy.utils`:
  * `CathVersion` to `cathpy.version`
  * simple classes to `cathpy.models`
  * util functions to `cathpy.tests`

## v0.0.1

### General

* first release
